    {
      "id": "PopularPost190990",
      "post_content": "Fortify seems neat, but prone to the same kinds of limitations that prevent Auras from seeing competitive play.  \n  \nStill, someday, I hope there will be a way to break this card. [Inkmoth Nexus](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Inkmoth Nexus) came close -- an indestructible flying blocker that leaves -1/-1 counters on your opponent's attacker is pretty cool. It's just not worth ![5](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=5&type=symbol). If this card said \"Fortified land is indestructible and gains shroud,\" then maybe.",
      "posted_by": "Salient",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost190990\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">Fortify seems neat, but prone to the same kinds of limitations that prevent Auras from seeing competitive play.<br/><br/>Still, someday, I hope there will be a way to break this card. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Inkmoth Nexus\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Inkmoth Nexus\">Inkmoth Nexus</a> came close -- an indestructible flying blocker that leaves -1/-1 counters on your opponent's attacker is pretty cool. It's just not worth <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"5\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=5&amp;type=symbol\"/>. If this card said \"Fortified land is indestructible and gains shroud,\" then maybe.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '190990'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy67559\">Salient</span>\r\n                                (8/25/2011 5:54:26 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl0